{"id":731,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":731,"title":"Isaiah 29","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 29"],[".studySummary",["i","A people (the Nephites) will speak as a voice from the dust—The Apostasy, restoration of the gospel, and coming forth of a sealed book (the Book of Mormon) are foretold—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27"},"2 Nephi 27"],"."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.1","order":"02.24.029.47309"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Woe"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Ariel"],", to Ariel, the city",["i",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"where"]],"David dwelt! add ye year to year; let them kill sacrifices."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.2","order":"02.24.029.47310"},["b","2"],"Yet I will distress Ariel, and there shall be heaviness and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"sorrow"],": and it shall be unto me as Ariel."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.3","order":"02.24.029.47311"},["b","3"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"camp"],"against thee round about, and will lay siege against thee with a mount, and I will raise forts against thee."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.4","order":"02.24.029.47312"},["b","4"],"And thou shalt be brought down,",["i","and"],"shalt speak out of the ground, and thy speech shall be low out of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"dust"],", and thy voice shall be, as of one that hath a familiar spirit, out of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"ground"],", and thy speech shall whisper out of the dust."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.5","order":"02.24.029.47313"},["b","5"],"Moreover the multitude of thy strangers shall be like small dust, and the multitude of the terrible ones",["i","shall be"],"as chaff that passeth away: yea, it shall be at an instant suddenly."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.6","order":"02.24.029.47314"},["b","6"],"Thou shalt be visited of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts with thunder, and with earthquake, and great noise, with storm and tempest, and the flame of devouring",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"fire"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.7","order":"02.24.029.47315"},["b","7"],"¶And the multitude of all the nations that fight against Ariel, even all that fight against her and her munition, and that distress her, shall be as a dream of a night vision."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.8","order":"02.24.029.47316"},["b","8"],"It shall even be as when an hungry",["i","man"],"dreameth, and, behold, he eateth; but he awaketh, and his soul is empty: or as when a thirsty man dreameth, and, behold, he drinketh; but he awaketh, and, behold,",["i","he is"],"faint, and his soul hath appetite: so shall the multitude of all the nations be, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"fight"],"against mount",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.9","order":"02.24.029.47317"},["b","9"],"¶Stay yourselves, and wonder; cry ye out, and cry: they are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"drunken"],", but not with wine; they stagger, but not with strong drink."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.10","order":"02.24.029.47318"},["b","10"],"For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath poured out upon you the spirit of deep",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"sleep"],", and hath closed your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"eyes"],": the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"prophets"],"and your rulers, the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"seers"],"hath he",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"covered"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.11","order":"02.24.029.47319"},["b","11"],"And the vision of all is become unto you as the words of a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"book"],"that is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"sealed"],", which",["i","men"],"deliver to one that is learned, saying, Read this, I pray thee: and he saith, I cannot; for it",["i","is"],"sealed:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.12","order":"02.24.029.47320"},["b","12"],"And the book is delivered to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"him"],"that is not learned, saying, Read this, I pray thee: and he saith, I am not learned."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13","order":"02.24.029.47321"},["b","13"],"¶Wherefore the Lord said, Forasmuch as this people",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"draw near"],["i","me"],"with their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"mouth"],", and with their lips do",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"honour"],"me, but have",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"removed"],"their",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_13e"},"heart"],"far from me, and their",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_13f"},"fear toward me"],"is taught by the",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_13g"},"precept"],"of men:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.14","order":"02.24.029.47322"},["b","14"],"Therefore, behold, I will proceed to do a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"marvellous"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"work"],"among this people,",["i","even"],"a marvellous work and a wonder: for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"wisdom"],"of their wise",["i","men"],"shall",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"perish"],", and the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"understanding"],"of their",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_14f"},"prudent"],["i","men"],"shall be hid."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.15","order":"02.24.029.47323"},["b","15"],"Woe unto them that seek deep to hide their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"counsel"],"from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and their works are in the dark, and they say, Who",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"seeth"],"us? and who knoweth us?"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.16","order":"02.24.029.47324"},["b","16"],"Surely your turning of things upside down shall be esteemed as the potter’s clay: for shall the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"work"],"say of him that made it, He made me not? or shall the thing framed say of him that framed it, He had no understanding?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.17","order":"02.24.029.47325"},["b","17"],["i","Is"],"it not yet a very little while, and Lebanon shall be turned into a fruitful field, and the fruitful field shall be esteemed as a forest?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.18","order":"02.24.029.47326"},["b","18"],"¶And in that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"day"],"shall the deaf hear the words of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"book"],", and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"eyes"],"of the blind shall see out of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"obscurity"],", and out of darkness."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.19","order":"02.24.029.47327"},["b","19"],"The meek also shall increase",["i","their"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"joy"],"in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"poor"],"among men shall rejoice in the Holy One of Israel."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.20","order":"02.24.029.47328"},["b","20"],"For the terrible one is brought to nought, and the scorner is consumed, and all that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"watch"],"for iniquity are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"cut off"],":"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.21","order":"02.24.029.47329"},["b","21"],"That make a man an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"offender"],"for a word, and lay a snare for him that reproveth in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"the gate"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"turn"],"aside the just for a thing of nought."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.22","order":"02.24.029.47330"},["b","22"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", who redeemed Abraham, concerning the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"house of Jacob"],", Jacob shall not now be ashamed, neither shall his face now wax pale."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.23","order":"02.24.029.47331"},["b","23"],"But when he seeth his children, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"work"],"of mine hands, in the midst of him, they shall sanctify my name, and sanctify the Holy One of Jacob, and shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"fear"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"God"],"of Israel."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.24","order":"02.24.029.47332"},["b","24"],"They also that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"erred"],"in spirit shall come to understanding, and they that murmured shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"learn"],"doctrine."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.1a","order":"02.24.029.47333"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-isa/29.1-8"},["span.small","JST"],"Isa. 29:1–8 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.1b","order":"02.24.029.47335"},["b","1b"],["span.small","HEB"],"Hearth of God; i.e., the temple; translated as “the altar” in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/43.15"},"Ezek. 43:15"],", second clause."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.1c","order":"02.24.029.47337"},["b","1c"],["span.small","IE"],"Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.2a","order":"02.24.029.47339"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorrow"},"TG Sorrow"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.3a","order":"02.24.029.47341"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.15"},"2 Ne. 26:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.4a","order":"02.24.029.47343"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.27"},"Moro. 10:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.4b","order":"02.24.029.47345"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-mormon"},"TG Book of Mormon"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.6a","order":"02.24.029.47347"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.26"},"D&C 97:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.8a","order":"02.24.029.47349"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/protection-divine"},"TG Protection, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.8b","order":"02.24.029.47351"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.9a","order":"02.24.029.47353"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.4"},"2 Ne. 27:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.10a","order":"02.24.029.47355"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/11.8.7-8"},"Rom. 11:8 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.10b","order":"02.24.029.47357"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.10c","order":"02.24.029.47359"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.5"},"2 Ne. 27:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.10d","order":"02.24.029.47361"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seer"},"TG Seer"],"."],["div",{"id":"10e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.10e","order":"02.24.029.47363"},["b","10e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/3.7"},"Micah 3:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.11a","order":"02.24.029.47365"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-mormon"},"TG Book of Mormon"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-to-come-forth"},"Scriptures to Come Forth"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.11b","order":"02.24.029.47367"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.7.6-26"},"2 Ne. 27:7 (6–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.65.63-65"},"JS—H 1:65 (63–65)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seal"},"TG Seal"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.12a","order":"02.24.029.47369"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.59"},"JS—H 1:59"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13a","order":"02.24.029.47371"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.19.5-26"},"JS—H 1:19 (5–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13b","order":"02.24.029.47373"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.31.30-33"},"Ezek. 33:31 (30–33)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13c","order":"02.24.029.47375"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/48.1"},"Isa. 48:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.8.7-9"},"Matt. 15:8 (7–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13d","order":"02.24.029.47377"},["b","13d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.13"},"Isa. 1:13"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"13e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13e","order":"02.24.029.47379"},["b","13e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heart"},"Heart"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worship"},"Worship"],"."],["div",{"id":"13f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13f","order":"02.24.029.47381"},["b","13f"],["span.small","OR"],"regard, reverence for me."],["div",{"id":"13g","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.13g","order":"02.24.029.47383"},["b","13g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/traditions-of-men"},"TG Traditions of Men"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.14a","order":"02.24.029.47385"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.8"},"1 Ne. 22:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/4.1"},"D&C 4:1"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-mormon"},"TG Book of Mormon"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/restoration-of-the-gospel"},"Restoration of the Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.14b","order":"02.24.029.47387"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-works-of"},"TG God, Works of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.14c","order":"02.24.029.47389"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wisdom"},"TG Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.14d","order":"02.24.029.47391"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.9"},"D&C 76:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"14e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.14e","order":"02.24.029.47393"},["b","14e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/knowledge"},"TG Knowledge"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/understanding"},"Understanding"],"."],["div",{"id":"14f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.14f","order":"02.24.029.47395"},["b","14f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prudence"},"TG Prudence"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.15a","order":"02.24.029.47397"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/counselor"},"TG Counselor"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.15b","order":"02.24.029.47399"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/47.10"},"Isa. 47:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.16a","order":"02.24.029.47401"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.9"},"Isa. 45:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/64.8"},"64:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.18a","order":"02.24.029.47403"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/last-days"},"TG Last Days"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.18b","order":"02.24.029.47405"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-mormon"},"TG Book of Mormon"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.18c","order":"02.24.029.47407"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/32.3"},"Isa. 32:3"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sight"},"TG Sight"],"."],["div",{"id":"18d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.18d","order":"02.24.029.47409"},["b","18d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/darkness-spiritual"},"TG Darkness, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.19a","order":"02.24.029.47411"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/joy"},"TG Joy"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.19b","order":"02.24.029.47413"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor"},"TG Poor"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.20a","order":"02.24.029.47415"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/12.10"},"Rev. 12:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.124"},"D&C 88:124"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watch"},"TG Watch"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.20b","order":"02.24.029.47417"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.50"},"D&C 45:50"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.21a","order":"02.24.029.47419"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/offense"},"TG Offense"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.21b","order":"02.24.029.47421"},["b","21b"],["span.small","IE"],"the place of public transactions."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.21c","order":"02.24.029.47423"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.12"},"Amos 5:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.22a","order":"02.24.029.47425"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/15.19.19-20"},"1 Ne. 15:19 (19–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.23a","order":"02.24.029.47427"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.11"},"Isa. 45:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.23b","order":"02.24.029.47429"},["b","23b"],["span.small","OR"],"stand in awe of the God of Israel."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.23c","order":"02.24.029.47431"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.3"},"Isa. 45:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.14"},"3 Ne. 11:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/36.1"},"D&C 36:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/127.3"},"127:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.24a","order":"02.24.029.47433"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.25"},"D&C 1:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/29.24b","order":"02.24.029.47435"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/learn"},"TG Learn"],"."]]}
